name: Viral 50 USA
content:
Description: viral 50 songs in the USA on spotify, data is updated everyday

Source: [Spotify](https://spotifycharts.com/viral/us/daily/latest)

Processing: downloaded .csv from spotify

Columns:

* Track Name (string): name of the song
* Artist (string): name of the artist of the song
* Position (numerical): ranking number of the song
